  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/87af7689787ac47f13a9758266db7af9.poster.avif?t=1766707895\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/87af7689787ac47f13a9758266db7af9.webm?t=1766707895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/87af7689787ac47f13a9758266db7af9.mp4?t=1766707895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/c955c3bd3b6b3783829755930c6467a1.webp?t=1766707895\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Agent Brain: Tricky Puzzle is a groundbreaking puzzle platformer that challenges youto think outside the box in ways you never imagined.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the limits of your creativity, and uncover its well-hidden secrets. Dive in and let each challenge inspire your next great solution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/34fff6f275c396df1619e981abf24103.webp?t=1766707895\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Every level introduces a unique solution method, breaking the fourth wall between the game and the player in unprecedented ways. From using a pause button to halt threats to turning off the sound to put an enemy NPC to sleep, the game continually surprises and engages players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/4418137394819a0f12c79559a1462b57.poster.avif?t=1766707895\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/4418137394819a0f12c79559a1462b57.webm?t=1766707895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/4418137394819a0f12c79559a1462b57.mp4?t=1766707895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>What to Expect in the Game:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Portal jumping</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Managing a flying drone companion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Driving a car</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dangerous traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jetpack flights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lasers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different super agent gadgets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And many other fun features that will keep your brain active</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/7e8b9d2b16686f69037ec05d8410d1d8.webp?t=1766707895\" width=616 height=50 /></span><i>\"We want this game to delight players at every level, ensuring they always experience that <strong>Aha! moment</strong>. That’s the essence we’re capturing here.\"</i> – dev team</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/fb1765e75e2c3469d133eeadb760231c.webp?t=1766707895\" width=616 height=50 /></span>In addition to the main puzzles, the game conceals well-hidden secrets that aren't so easy to uncover, adding an extra layer of challenge for those daring enough to seek them out.<br></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/87af7689787ac47f13a9758266db7af9.poster.avif?t=1766707895\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/87af7689787ac47f13a9758266db7af9.webm?t=1766707895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/87af7689787ac47f13a9758266db7af9.mp4?t=1766707895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/c955c3bd3b6b3783829755930c6467a1.webp?t=1766707895\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Agent Brain: Tricky Puzzle is a groundbreaking puzzle platformer that challenges youto think outside the box in ways you never imagined.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the limits of your creativity, and uncover its well-hidden secrets. Dive in and let each challenge inspire your next great solution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/34fff6f275c396df1619e981abf24103.webp?t=1766707895\" width=616 height=50 /></span>Every level introduces a unique solution method, breaking the fourth wall between the game and the player in unprecedented ways. From using a pause button to halt threats to turning off the sound to put an enemy NPC to sleep, the game continually surprises and engages players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863350/extras/4418137394819a0f12c79559a1462b57.poster.avif?t=1766707895\" width=600 heigh